{"tid":1002393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(支爆有片)中國高鐵債務全球第一","createTime":"2019-01-31T01:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T01:42:44.000Z","uid":104804,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed204dcd6eb4c102a85d2852408f328867fcc64","tid":1002393,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:56:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1881211358655723/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1881211358655723%2F&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6rktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=6eb09db3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1881211358655723/</a><br />\n<br />\n交通運輸學者提醒中國高鐵債務全球第一】<br />\n【部分路線可能連電費都付不起】<br />\n<br />\n高鐵是中國官方近年最引以為傲的基建，高鐵的宣傳片強調「中國高鐵總里程在2018年底達到2.9萬公里，佔世界高鐵總量三分之二；電氣化率、客運周轉量、貨運發送量、換算周轉量和運輸密度等指標，位居世界第一。」但同時，有學者提醒，中國高鐵的債務和營運虧損亦是世界第一。<br />\n<br />\n北京交通大學經濟管理學院教授趙堅：「2.9萬公里的高鐵是世界上其他地區的兩倍，那都是靠借錢建的。」<br />\n<br />\n趙堅指中鐵總的前身鐵道部在2005年已負債4768億元，到2016年更爆增到4.72萬億元，11年內翻了九倍，當中近七成債務都是用來建設高鐵，每年要付利息1568億元。同年，中鐵總的客運收入有2817億元，估算高鐵收入佔一半，有1409億元，都未夠支付利息。<br />\n<br />\n除了債務過多，趙堅提醒，高鐵賺不了錢亦是問題所在，目前除了京滬和京廣高鐵，大部分中西部的高鐵都是閒置狀態。「因為它人口沒那麼多，比如像最典型的是蘭新線，它沿途都是沙漠，它也建了這個蘭新高鐵，差不多1700多公里，現在每天只開行四對車，所以我估計它連電費都付不起的。」<br />\n<br />\n而即使是運輸密度最高的京滬高鐵，與日本新幹線相比仍有很大差距。整個中國高鐵的平均運輸密度，只有新幹線的一半。趙堅指，官方不應再建太多高鐵，特別是中西部，否則國民經濟的運行效率就會降低，他建議利用同樣的資源建更多普通鐵路。<br />\n<br />\n#高鐵債務<br />\n#厲害了我的鐵<br />\n#打貪<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"3ca78f67335912c9f6187ef8279e3234a9cc2da9","tid":1002393,"uid":104804,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T01:58:02.000Z","msg":"全民大煉鋼(高鐵)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125dd274f23dfc74829c5672df77b139dcb8f9bc","tid":1002393,"uid":141151,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:00:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#厲害了我的鐵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e1ffb2d6e46a0d91ea580862b1c52ebaf32227","tid":1002393,"uid":52946,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"125dd274f23dfc74829c5672df77b139dcb8f9bc","tid":1002393,"uid":141151,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:00:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#厲害了我的鐵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c97034c2f19976fa592f723c65889a1cfc9403c","tid":1002393,"uid":43428,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:04:28.000Z","msg":"起埋d爛銅爛鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"968543cdeb014a8da373b8720491ff195c6d4efe","tid":1002393,"uid":104804,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9c97034c2f19976fa592f723c65889a1cfc9403c","tid":1002393,"uid":43428,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:04:28.000Z","msg":"起埋d爛銅爛鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"21世紀大躍進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec54fe76eb8b8b192e9681aec965d52b7f12f9d","tid":1002393,"uid":21378,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T02:16:01.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋都係蝕 勁少車行。<br />\n益咗班黃牛炒過橋証<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859a4325a0e79c4c0b7c9298996fd1b70eb7b2cf","tid":1002393,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4e1ffb2d6e46a0d91ea580